                <p>
                    - <a href="sign-up">Create an account</a> or <a href="log-in">log in</a> to start using &nbsp;&nbsp;our services.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
                <h3>Choose Service</h3>
                <p>
                    - Select the service you need from our wide &nbsp;&nbsp;range of offerings.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
                <h3>Make Payment</h3>
                <p>
                    - Securely pay for your selected service
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;using various payment methods.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <h3>Receive Confirmation</h3>
